        <name xml:lang="en">agricultural trailer</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">agricultural trailer is used as a proxy for harvesting cart. The cart has an operational time of 0.001605h/ha (2021 Nebraska Crop budget projections, Robert Klein and Glennis McClure, UNL Extension). The trailer has a lifetime operational time of 1200h, and it weights 1500 kg. Based on FAOSTAT data, 2020 the yield of maize in the US is 107945 hg/ha = 10794,5 kg/ha</comment>
